<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to MotoShare</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #242424;
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    table {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        height: 100%;
        background-color: rgb(36, 36, 36);
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    .title, table h1 {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 46px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }

    table td {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    table img {
        max-width: 80%;
        height: auto;
    }

    table p {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }

    .content-header-1 {
        width: 90%;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .content-header-2 {
        background-color: rgb(219, 238, 255);
        border-radius: 25px;
        width: 90%;
        height: 50px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 32px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: black;
    }

    table .info {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }

    table .guide {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }

    table ul {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }

    table ul li {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 5px 0;
    }

    table .footer {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding-top: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
    }

    table .footer a {
        width: 100%;
        color: rgb(147, 112, 219);
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    table .copyright {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: rgb(119, 119, 119);
    }

    .table-row-dark td {
        background-color: rgb(41, 41, 41);
        border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;
    }

    .table-row-light td {
        background-color: rgb(41, 41, 41);
        border-radius: 0 0 15px 15px;
    }
</style>
<body bgcolor="#242424">
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" class="title">
                <h1>{{title}}</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <img src="{{motorbikeImageUrl}}" alt="Motorbike">
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <p class="content-header-1">{{userName}}, your validation code is : </p>
                <p class="content-header-2">{{validationCode}}</p>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr class="table-row-dark">
            <td>
                <p class="info">
                    This authentication code will be expired within 10 minutes, please don't release this code to other people.
                </p>
                <p class="guide">A quick guide to start your travel:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Select your start position and end position on built-in Google Map.</li>
                    <li>Provide some extra information such as payment, descriptions.</li>
                    <li>Select existing orders to directly start your travel.</li>
                    <li>Or create your custom purchase orders to let riders know what you want.</li>
                    <li>Once the riders invite you, the app will send a notification to you.</li>
                    <li>Then you can accept it if it meets your demand, or reject it if it doesn't.</li>
                    <li>Now, you can enjoy your travel! Don't forget to leave a comment once done.</li>
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="table-row-light">
            <td class="footer">
                <p>
                    The app is still not in the official version, if there's any problem with the app, please contact me with this email:
                    <a href="mailto:motoshare767@gmail.com">motoshare767@gmail.com</a>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <p class="copyright">Â© {{currentYear}} MotoShare Inc.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
